<p>Use background opacity utility classes to control the transparency
level of background colors. These utilities can be used in conjunction
with background color <code>bg-[color]</code> definitions.</p>
<h3 id="syntax">Syntax</h3>
<pre class="html"><code>.bg-opacity-[value]</code></pre>
